NFS (EFS is used NFS technology)
Supports Pay as you Go model
Scales on demand, perfomance is not affected at all
EFS Volume can be attached/mounted with multiple EC2 Instances /
No Capacity Limitation - Scalable upto Petabyte 

Security Group must be same for both EC2 Instance, Storage - Security group must allow NFS protocol

